				'**Finding the matching LANDSEJERLAVNR
				If NOT bReCalled Then
					If NOT SRCHShowMatchValueInListControl(SRCH_CTRL_MATR_LANDSELAV_LIST, marrssdInfo(nCtrlItem).szTab,
							marrssdInfo(nCtrlItem).szCol, marrssdInfo(4).szCol, marrssdInfo(nCtrlItem).szCond, marrValues4) Then
					
